01:18.132 --> 01:21.721
Do you know how much I have missed this?

01:21.722 --> 01:24.721
A lot?

01:24.722 --> 01:26.632
Yeah.

01:28.802 --> 01:31.172
A lot.

01:41.012 --> 01:43.551
Hey.

01:43.552 --> 01:45.671
Hey.

01:45.672 --> 01:46.671
Hey.

01:46.672 --> 01:47.671
What?

01:47.672 --> 01:49.171
Rayna.

01:49.172 --> 01:51.261
Hey, sleepyhead.

01:51.262 --> 01:53.971
You planning on getting up today?

01:53.972 --> 01:56.011
Yeah.

01:56.012 --> 01:56.972
I'll see you downstairs.

01:56.973 --> 01:59.472
Take your time. Thanks, babe.

02:10.051 --> 02:11.841
♪ Everybody knows what's going down ♪

02:11.842 --> 02:13.171
Miss Barnes!

02:13.172 --> 02:16.721
Miss Barnes!

02:16.722 --> 02:18.511
Yes?

02:18.512 --> 02:21.671
Lord, what'd my mama do now?

02:21.672 --> 02:23.931
Look, if you want her,
just... You can take her.

02:23.932 --> 02:25.381
She's all yours.

02:25.382 --> 02:27.431
We actually came for you.

02:27.432 --> 02:28.971
What the hell is this?

02:28.972 --> 02:31.011
Shoplifting is a class "a" misdemeanor.

02:31.012 --> 02:32.761
I'm sure by now you've seen the video.

02:32.762 --> 02:35.051
About 4 million people have.

02:37.882 --> 02:38.971
Seriously?

02:38.972 --> 02:41.051
Get a real job.

02:41.052 --> 02:44.881
♪ God, I've done it now ♪

02:44.882 --> 02:46.801
Will you tell me
what's really happening

02:46.802 --> 02:48.721
with the polls with Teddy?

02:48.722 --> 02:50.931
He's always so upbeat with me.

02:50.932 --> 02:52.301
He's down 12 points.

02:52.302 --> 02:53.971
No. Are you serious?

02:53.972 --> 02:56.011
Rayna, he is practically on life support.

02:56.012 --> 02:58.511
Hey, girls, ten minutes.

02:58.512 --> 02:59.931
I don't think she can hear you.

02:59.932 --> 03:01.721
No, she heard you.

03:01.722 --> 03:03.221
It's called selective listening.

03:03.222 --> 03:06.761
I was texting Virginia about my homework.

03:06.762 --> 03:08.551
See, I told you she could hear me.

03:08.552 --> 03:10.221
Aunt Tandy, daddy's gonna win, right?

03:10.222 --> 03:11.552
Absolutely.

03:14.632 --> 03:16.011
He has a fund-Raiser this weekend.

03:16.012 --> 03:19.011
Really? I could sing.

03:19.012 --> 03:20.631
You sing? Yes, I sing.

03:20.632 --> 03:22.591
You should sing. I could sing.
Would that help?

03:22.592 --> 03:25.971
Well, Teddy wouldn't say so,
But, yes, that would help.

03:25.972 --> 03:27.971
Easy. Done. Just tell me where and when.

03:27.972 --> 03:30.011
It's at the country club.

03:30.012 --> 03:31.221
No. Mom.

03:31.222 --> 03:32.631
Mom, there's this video online.

03:32.632 --> 03:33.801
You're not gonna believe it.

03:33.802 --> 03:36.592
It's about Juliette Barnes.

03:40.382 --> 03:41.971
4 million views. Not bad.

03:41.972 --> 03:44.171
Yes, she's seen it, because
everybody's seen it.

03:44.172 --> 03:45.488
Baby, you got any more cereal?

03:45.489 --> 03:47.929
All right, well, just come to
the house when you land, okay?

03:47.930 --> 03:49.530
At least something made without raisins.

03:49.531 --> 03:50.491
You know I hate raisins.

03:50.492 --> 03:52.092
All right, Makena's on her way to J.F.K.

03:52.093 --> 03:53.511
Makena? Yeah.

03:53.512 --> 03:55.881
Why? Doesn't she have Kristen
Stewart to worry about?

03:55.882 --> 03:58.261
When you're at the center
of a publicity nightmare,

03:58.262 --> 03:59.761
you generally need your publicist.

03:59.762 --> 04:02.091
- You're kidding me, baby.
- You got no milk.

04:02.092 --> 04:04.841
I cannot believe she has to stay here.

04:04.842 --> 04:06.551
After everything that's transpired

04:06.552 --> 04:08.801
in the last 48 hours, that's
what you can't believe?

04:08.802 --> 04:10.931
You know what, Glenn? You need to relax.

04:10.932 --> 04:13.092
As Makena would say, any
publicity is good publicity.

04:13.093 --> 04:15.472
Yeah, well, I don't
think she'd say that.

04:16.841 --> 04:18.051
At least I look good.

04:27.932 --> 04:29.221
Hey.

04:29.222 --> 04:30.221
Hey. How was your day?

04:30.222 --> 04:31.221
It was long.

04:31.222 --> 04:33.261
They make you show up at 6:00.

04:33.262 --> 04:35.131
Turns out there's some noise ordinance.

04:35.132 --> 04:36.332
Couldn't even start TILL 8:00.

04:36.333 --> 04:38.841
How about you?

04:38.842 --> 04:40.221
Uneventful. Yeah?

04:40.222 --> 04:41.622
Waiting on news that's never coming

04:41.623 --> 04:42.983
from a phone that's never ringing.

04:42.984 --> 04:44.301
Well, look, just the fact

04:44.302 --> 04:46.381
that you got to record a
demo with watty white...

04:46.382 --> 04:48.841
I mean, people would kill
for that opportunity.

04:48.842 --> 04:50.801
I know. I know.

04:50.802 --> 04:53.171
All you can control is
what you put out there,

04:53.172 --> 04:56.631
not whether some publisher
will be interested.

04:56.632 --> 04:58.272
Yeah, well, I just wish They'd tell me no

04:58.273 --> 04:59.593
so I could put it out of my mind.

04:59.594 --> 05:02.972
Well... if you really wanna
put it out of your mind...

05:07.632 --> 05:09.221
Anyone home? Gunnar.

05:10.802 --> 05:13.131
Seriously?

05:13.132 --> 05:14.171
Hey.

05:14.172 --> 05:16.972
Hey.

05:18.842 --> 05:21.301
Sorry to just show up like this,

05:21.302 --> 05:23.761
but I thought you'd wanna
know as soon as I'd heard.

05:23.762 --> 05:25.761
What?

05:25.762 --> 05:27.761
We got the deal.

05:27.762 --> 05:29.841
Are you serious? No.

05:29.842 --> 05:33.131
No? He's messing with you.

05:33.132 --> 05:34.841
I'm messing with you. We got the deal!

05:34.842 --> 05:35.931
don't you mess with me!

05:35.932 --> 05:39.051
I'm so excited! We got a deal!

05:41.222 --> 05:43.381
My god. I can't believe it.

05:45.012 --> 05:47.971
♪ Dreaming about me ♪

05:47.972 --> 05:49.302
Hey.

05:51.342 --> 05:53.261
Hey.

05:53.262 --> 05:54.511
So I heard a rumor today

05:54.512 --> 05:56.261
that you're gonna be doing a set for me

05:56.262 --> 05:59.051
at the country club. Well, I
hope it's more than a rumor.

05:59.052 --> 06:00.972
And I hope they're putting
out a press release.

06:00.973 --> 06:03.431
That's why I'm doing it. They did.

06:03.432 --> 06:05.051
And thanks.

06:05.052 --> 06:06.971
I really mean it.

06:06.972 --> 06:11.051
Babe... You know you can tell
me if things aren't going well.

06:11.052 --> 06:13.511
Things are going fine.

06:15.672 --> 06:18.051
All right, well...

06:18.052 --> 06:20.011
12 points down doesn't exactly sound fine.

06:20.012 --> 06:22.091
Hon, who... Who told you that?

06:22.092 --> 06:23.881
My sister.

06:23.882 --> 06:24.971
The mouth of the south.

06:24.972 --> 06:26.261
Right. She's also the one

06:26.262 --> 06:27.748
who told me about this fund-Raiser.

06:27.749 --> 06:29.989
Okay. That's internal polling
that she's talking about,

06:29.990 --> 06:31.430
and there is a huge margin of error.

06:31.431 --> 06:33.431
All right, But if you're
not telling me anything,

06:33.432 --> 06:36.801
then she's the only one
I've got to listen to.

06:36.802 --> 06:37.990
Coming home and telling you

06:37.991 --> 06:39.431
about everything that's going wrong,

06:39.432 --> 06:42.631
the... the... the country club,
your dad being involved...

06:42.632 --> 06:44.132
Honey, I'm just trying to spare you.

06:45.882 --> 06:48.011
Well, I appreciate that.

06:48.012 --> 06:49.532
And, you know, I was gonna talk to you

06:49.533 --> 06:50.973
about this whole country club venue.

06:50.974 --> 06:52.454
Maybe we can think about changing it.

06:52.455 --> 06:54.591
I mean, I can sing anywhere, hon.

06:54.592 --> 06:56.431
I can sing at the airport...

06:56.432 --> 06:58.171
Mars.

06:58.172 --> 07:00.631
Hell. There you go.

07:00.632 --> 07:03.134
Connecticut.

07:03.135 --> 07:05.935
Yes, we know. Of course. A disturbing
subject for a lot of parents...

07:05.936 --> 07:08.256
We called Makena. No doubt
you've all seen or heard about

07:08.257 --> 07:10.417
country star Juliette Barnes'
shoplifting incident...

07:10.418 --> 07:11.938
tomorrow, I guess.
Baby, lookit here.

07:11.939 --> 07:12.579
There's at least

07:12.580 --> 07:14.178
20 different kinds of nail polish in here,

07:14.179 --> 07:15.019
all different colors.

07:15.020 --> 07:16.620
Now why on earth do you go and steal 'em

07:16.621 --> 07:17.781
when you have all these here?

07:17.782 --> 07:19.471
Why don't you just mind your own business?

07:21.262 --> 07:22.761
Can't you do something with her,

07:22.762 --> 07:24.631
like send her back to Birmingham?

07:24.632 --> 07:26.551
That's for the judge to
decide at her hearing.

07:26.552 --> 07:28.841
I can't do anything. What, in seven weeks?

07:28.842 --> 07:30.841
Can't you do something? Pull some strings?

07:30.842 --> 07:32.591
Tell them who I am.

07:32.592 --> 07:35.511
Doubt that'll do much Good right now.

07:40.222 --> 07:42.011
I can't be around her for another second.

07:42.012 --> 07:44.051
There she is! I see her! The thief!

07:44.052 --> 07:45.671
You've been stealing!

07:48.762 --> 07:51.091
You've gotta be kidding me.

07:51.092 --> 07:53.671
Stay down. Just stay down.

07:53.672 --> 07:55.011
I think we should turn around.

07:56.222 --> 07:58.171
This is a nightmare.

08:04.709 --> 08:07.674
